title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps NFL Cutdown day. There's some stats attached to a couple of the players released yesterday. Vikings new Head Coach Kevin O'Connell shares his outlook on his team going into this season. And Brady Quinn throws his hat in the rink to join us for our Dublin trip next August.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
